RESULT - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan
If a barcode is found, Barcodes returns android.app.Activity#RESULT_OK to android.app.Activity#onActivityResult(int, int, android.content.Intent) of the app which requested the scan via android.app.Activity#startActivityForResult(android.content.Intent, int) The barcodes contents can be retrieved with android.content.Intent#getStringExtra(String).

Prefix for keys that map to the values of ResultMetadataType.BYTE_SEGMENTS, if available.
RESULT_BYTES - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan
Call android.content.Intent#getByteArrayExtra(String) with RESULT_BYTES to get a byte[] of raw bytes in the barcode, if available.
RESULT_DISPLAY_DURATION_MS - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan
Desired duration in milliseconds for which to pause after a successful scan before returning to the calling intent.
RESULT_ERROR_CORRECTION_LEVEL - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan

RESULT_FORMAT - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan

RESULT_ORIENTATION - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan

RESULT_UPC_EAN_EXTENSION - 类 中的静态变量com.king.zxing.Intents.Scan
